  "text": "This section presents comparison results with three other approximation algorithms for comparison that we implemented, namely simple random sampling (adapted from [CITATION_1] , stratified coalition sampling (adapted from [CITATION_2] , and learning stratified sampling (adapted from [CITATION_3] . We apply the Linear Programming Sensitivity Analysis technique for the calculation of marginal contributions in all algorithms. A brief review of the different steps among these sampling techniques was given in Section 2.4.",
